The Royal Enfield Himalayan 450 is a modern adventure bike featuring a new liquid-cooled 452cc Sherpa engine (40bhp/40Nm), ride-by-wire,
 a circular TFT screen with Google Maps, and switchable ABS, offering better off-road capability and touring comfort than its predecessor, with a strong mid-range but som
e initial flatness and vibrations at highway speeds, built on a new chassis with quality Showa suspension.
 Key aspects include its 21/17-inch wheel setup, 17L tank
